headline: Why Super Micro Computer Stock Is Soaring Today
summary: Super Micro Computer (NASDAQ: SMCI) stock is rocketing higher Wednesday in response to multiple positive catalysts.  At the same point in the session, the S&P 500 had risen 1.8%, and the Nasdaq Composite was up 2.9%.  Supermicro's valuation is climbing today thanks to a combination of encouraging developments on the macroeconomic front.
